@code {
    string userInput = "";
    bool isLightOn = false;

    void CheckCondition()
    {
        // Convert user input to lowercase and check
        if (userInput.Trim().ToLower() == "on")
        {
            isLightOn = true;
        }
        else
        {
            isLightOn = false;
        }
    } i want both as a button type like true button and false button  on the screen itself also no need of      text box remove it  
